---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Support PhilaCon Valley - Donate"
  description="Support PhilaCon Valley's mission to make Philadelphia a tech hub by us, for us. Your donation keeps events free and accessible."
>
  <Header />

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 to-accent-600 text-white py-20">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">Support Our Mission</h1>
        <p class="text-2xl opacity-90">
          Help keep PhilaCon Valley free and accessible for everyone
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Support -->
  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Why Your Support Matters</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8 text-center">
          PhilaCon Valley is committed to keeping all events free and accessible. We believe
          financial barriers shouldn't prevent anyone from learning tech skills and building
          their career. Your support makes this possible.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-12">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
              </svg>
              Event Venues
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Rent spaces like Pennovation Works that provide the infrastructure for hands-on
              collaboration and workshops.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
              </svg>
              Learning Resources
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Create and share free tutorials, workshops materials, and educational content
              for the community.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9" />
              </svg>
              Infrastructure
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Maintain website, tools, and platforms that help the community connect,
              collaborate, and grow.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
              </svg>
              Community Growth
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Support outreach efforts to connect with more underrepresented folks in tech
              across Philadelphia.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Open Collective Section -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Support via Open Collective</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8">
          We use Open Collective for transparent, community-driven financial management.
          You can see exactly how every dollar is spent and the impact it makes.
        </p>

        <!-- Open Collective Embed -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 mb-8">
          <div class="mb-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Make a Contribution</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
              One-time or recurring donations – every amount helps keep our events free and accessible.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Open Collective Widget Placeholder -->
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-50 to-accent-50 rounded-lg p-12 mb-6">
            <p class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4">Support us on Open Collective</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
              Visit our Open Collective page to make a one-time or recurring contribution.
              All transactions are transparent and publicly visible.
            </p>
            <Button href="https://opencollective.com/philacon-valley" external variant="primary" size="lg">
              Donate on Open Collective
            </Button>
          </div>

          <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">
            <p class="mb-2">✓ Fully transparent – see how funds are used</p>
            <p class="mb-2">✓ Secure payment processing</p>
            <p>✓ Tax-deductible receipts available</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Other Ways to Support -->
  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Other Ways to Support</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Sponsor an Event</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Companies and organizations can sponsor specific events. Your support covers
              venue costs, refreshments, and materials while gaining visibility with our community.
            </p>
            <Button href="/contact" variant="outline">
              Inquire About Sponsorship
            </Button>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Volunteer as a Mentor</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Share your expertise by mentoring community members, leading workshops, or
              supporting Collab Lab sessions.
            </p>
            <Button href="/join" variant="outline">
              Get Involved
            </Button>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Provide Venue Space</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Do you have space we could use for events? Help us bring tech education to more
              people across Philadelphia.
            </p>
            <Button href="/contact" variant="outline">
              Offer Venue Space
            </Button>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Share Job Opportunities</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Hiring? Share inclusive job opportunities with our community. We especially welcome
              roles from companies committed to diversity and equity.
            </p>
            <Button href="/contact" variant="outline">
              Post a Job
            </Button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-accent-600 text-white">
    <div class="container-custom text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Make an Impact?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto opacity-90">
        Your support helps us build the Philadelphia tech community we want to see.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <Button href="https://opencollective.com/philacon-valley" external variant="secondary" size="lg">
          Donate Now
        </Button>
        <Button href="/contact" variant="outline" size="lg" class="!text-white !border-white hover:!bg-white/10">
          Other Ways to Help
        </Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
